School Data Enrichment Project Documentation

Overview
--------
This project is designed to enrich school data by:
1. Retrieving schools from a Supabase database
2. Scraping additional information from school review websites
3. Geocoding school addresses to obtain precise coordinates
4. Updating the database with the enriched data

The project uses a combination of direct database access, web scraping, and geocoding tools, orchestrated by AI agents using the crewAI framework.

